text: Potro watambula ekahiso ke pepe toke apa akasi, pwayi watela okutyuka ko mapalo.
translated_text: Umbundu: Potro watambula ekahiso ke pepe toke apa akasi, pwayi watela okutyuka ko mapalo. English: The cows are busy in the fields, but they are not busy in the fields.

text: Cikwavo vali, nda kwacilingile okakwata ovitangi vyalwa: esamwo lyalwa lyokuyova, ukopo kwenda, k’esulilo, okufa.
translated_text: Umbundu: Cikwavo vali, nda kwacilingile okakwata ovitangi vyalwa: esamwo lyalwa lyokuyova, ukopo kwenda, k’esulilo, okufa. English: I’m going to go to the market, but I’m not going to buy anything.

text: Olondingupange vyolupale wo Amestardão kwenda onjo yokumõla oviñgumañguma vyasonẽhiwa Anne Frank vapopya okuti utiukwete ovipuka kwenda imõlisa esakalaso k’omwenyo yowiñgi, kaliye vapopya okuti vakala ocipepi k’okupuka.
translated_text: Umbundu: Olondingupange vyolupale wo Amestardão kwenda onjo yokumõla oviñgumañguma vyasonẽhiwa Anne Frank vapopya okuti utiukwete ovipuka kwenda imõlisa esakalaso k’omwenyo yowiñgi, kaliye vapopya okuti vakala ocipepi k’okupuka. English: Anne Frank’s Diary, a book by Anne Frank, published in the United States in 1942.

text: Osipitali yakwama ovihandeleo viteta esambuko lyuveyi, c’avelapo etepiso lyombeyi k’olombeyi vikwavo oco citave okupopela vana kavasangiwa luveyi yavakwavo.
translated_text: Umbundu: Osipitali yakwama ovihandeleo viteta esambuko lyuveyi, c’avelapo etepiso lyombeyi k’olombeyi vikwavo oco citave okupopela vana kavasangiwa luveyi yavakwavo. English: Osipitali is a village in the Ondo District of the Ondo State in Nigeria.

text: Vatyuka konyima ovita eci valwa veya le pute okwambatisako mbutika, atendelo va 40 vasyala noke kavatavele okutyuka kokamenga yavo.
translated_text: Umbundu: Vatyuka konyima ovita eci valwa veya le pute okwambatisako mbutika, atendelo va 40 vasyala noke kavatavele okutyuka kokamenga yavo. English: The woman who is pregnant does not have to give birth to a child.

text: Asakuli vafetika okuvilikiwa kusoma Augusto kwenda toke eci vatunga ohongele yatete yesaku yo Roma oco citave okukaya omanu k’endiso lyuyaki.

text: Kaliye, endisi wakwata apunene anene calwa vutwe.
translated_text: Umbundu: Kaliye, endisi wakwata apunene anene calwa vutwe. English: Kaliye, the chief of the Umbundu people, is the chief of the endisi of the Umbundu people.

text: Eye wamisako hati, “Tukwete kaliye olomuku vikwete olosaĩ vikualã, viakala londiambete okuti kavikwete vali”.
translated_text: Umbundu: Eye wamisako hati, “Tukwete kaliye olomuku vikwete olosaĩ vikualã, viakala londiambete okuti kavikwete vali”. English: Eye wamisako hati, “We must be careful not to let our guard down, so that we do not become a victim of our own success”.

text: Ovihemba viponda nda vyaciwa pokati k’etimba kacitava okucimõla l’ovaso. Ayevalo l’okusanja vimõlisa okuti k’okukulĩha uveyi omanu vakwete hacitava mekonda okucilinga civala.
translated_text: Umbundu: Ovihemba viponda nda vyaciwa pokati k’etimba kacitava okucimõla l’ovaso. Ayevalo l’okusanja vimõlisa okuti k’okukulĩha uveyi omanu vakwete hacitava mekonda okucilinga civala. English: Ovihemba viponda nda vyaciwa pokati k’etimba kacitava okucimõla l’ovaso. Ayevalo l’okusanja vimõlisa nokuk’okukušiliha uveyi nokucilinga civala.

text: Lekumbululo, olonjimbi vasipa epangwe k’opaluku, kwenda ocipito caco ikasi l’okweca ongunsu k’omanu oco vatale.

translated_text: Umbundu: V’esapulo, oco okwate ovina vyalwa, enda lo-fole l’ongusu yalwa ale l’onjanga yalwa. English: The monkey is a big, fat, fat monkey.

translated_text: Umbundu: Citava calwa ciwa okumõla olopilamide v’okutekãva kwenda okuvimõla v’okũha k’efetiko lyocipito. English: “I’m going to go to the library to read.”

text: Esfinge likapiwa ndonanga yikapiwa k’ombwelo kwenda una otetulula esapulo limwe.
translated_text: Umbundu: Esfinge likapiwa ndonanga yikapiwa k’ombwelo kwenda una otetulula esapulo limwe. English: The elephant is a symbol of the power of the people.

text: Kuli olofeto vimwe vyokweca okulya, okunywa kwenda okupapala, oco citave okukwata akombe l’ovinjola k’omẽla kwenda luhayele walwa okuvãha cosi vasukila.

text: Konele yaye kwalepa ko vali o ciclone itukwiwa onjeke imwe yo ndende kelimi lya Maldivas, ya mamako 240º km la kukuto (149 kolomilha vakukutu).

translated_text: Umbundu: Onepa yo Turquia, okukapa oviva, visoka 783.562 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (300.948 sq mi) kuna 755.688 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (291.773 sq mi) oco kaliye ko sudoeste Asiático kwenda 23.764 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (9.174 sq mi) vo Europa. English: Onepa yo Turks, okukapa oviva, visoka 783.562 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (300.948 sq mi) kuna 755.688 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (291.773 sq mi) oco kaliye ko sudoeste Asiático kwenda 23.764 k’olokilometulu vikwãla (9.174 sq mi) vo Europa.

text: Ofeka ina yañgwlĩwa lovava vakalunga conepa yombwelo, yasangwya kulima 1819, valivangwila enconda lyoongwelo vinene kefetikilo lyalima 2020.
translated_text: Umbundu: Ofeka ina yañgwlĩwa lovava vakalunga conepa yombwelo, yasangwya kulima 1819, valivangwila enconda lyoongwelo vinene kefetikilo lyalima 2020. English: Ofeka ina yañgwpẹla lovava vakalunga conepa yombwelo, yasangwya kulima 1819, valivangwila enconda lyoongwelo vinene kefetikilo lyalima 2020.

text: Apia okapitale yolupale yo Samoa. Olupale isangiwa ocipãla ko ilya lyo Upolu kwenda ikwete owiñgi usoka etendelo lyasoka 40.000 lyomanu.
translated_text: Umbundu: Apia okapitale yolupale yo Samoa. Olupale isangiwa ocipãla ko ilya lyo Upolu kwenda ikwete owiñgi usoka etendelo lyasoka 40.000 lyomanu. English: The Samoan language is spoken in the islands of the Samoan archipelago.

text: Ndomo ofela ikasi kupala oco ipume onele yo kalunga, co ngo okuvanja unene ko Estados Unidos ale Caribe.
translated_text: Umbundu: Ndomo ofela ikasi kupala oco ipume onele yo kalunga, co ngo okuvanja unene ko Estados Unidos ale Caribe. English: Ndomo ofela ikasi kupala oco ipume onele yo kalunga, co ngo okuvanja unene ko Estados Unidos ale Caribe.

text: Waliyula po momo cacolele doto ndosi vina vyalepa.
translated_text: Umbundu: Waliyula po momo cacolele doto ndosi vina vyalepa. English: The people of Umbundu are very proud of their culture.

text: Esisi lina ko obmanguezais kuli vamwe ovitibvikwavo vikwete onguso vina visikilila usenge ale o plinicie Gangetica.
translated_text: Umbundu: Esisi lina ko obmanguezais kuli vamwe ovitibvikwavo vikwete onguso vina visikilila usenge ale o plinicie Gangetica. English: The Esisi is a witchcraft ritual that is performed by the people of Umbundu in the north of the country.

text: Etaliso limõlisa olo-sismo visangiwa kupange wo-Geologia vo-EUA kayamõlisile osismo layimwe vo Islândia k’osemana yapita.
translated_text: Umbundu: Etaliso limõlisa olo-sismo visangiwa kupange wo-Geologia vo-EUA kayamõlisile osismo layimwe vo Islândia k’osemana yapita. English: And so it is that the geologists have been studying the volcanic eruptions in the Andes for the past two decades.

text: Okupuyuka komunda yesinha ya Meca eleva lya tekava ko lwali lwosi.
translated_text: Umbundu: Okupuyuka komunda yesinha ya Meca eleva lya tekava ko lwali lwosi. English: The village of Meca in Umbundu is a high-rise building.
